author: makortel
body:
#### PR description:

This PR suggests to remove `IgProfModule`. From history in https://github.com/cms-cvs-history/IgTools-IgProf this seems to have been replaced with `IgProfService` long time ago. Also twiki searches show nothing on `IgProfModule`, while `IgProfService` gets hits.

Resolves https://github.com/makortel/framework/issues/207

#### PR validation:

None
title: Remove IgProfModule as obsolete
